article.description: — Ziggy Reid registered 16 points as Merrimack beat St. Francis (Pa.) 68-62 on Thursday.
article.headline: Reid lifts Merrimack over St Francis (Pa) 68-62
article.linkText: Reid lifts Merrimack over St Francis (Pa) 68-62
article.story: NORTH ANDOVER, Mass. -- — Ziggy Reid registered 16 points as Merrimack beat St. Francis (Pa.) 68-62 on Thursday. Devin Jensen had 13 points and eight rebounds for Merrimack (5-4, 5-4 Northeast Conference). Mikey Watkins added 11 points, six rebounds and six assists. Josh Cohen and Ramiir Dixon-Conover each had 13 points for the Red Flash (5-11, 4-8). Myles Thompson had 11 points and eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
